                <p class="project-brief">Zaawansowana platforma e-commerce z AI recommendations</p>
                <div class="project-tech">
                  <span class="tech-tag">React</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">Node.js</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">AI</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-info">
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="project-type">E-COMMERCE</span>
              <span class="project-year">2024</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="project-name">E-commerce Revolution</h3>
            <p class="project-description">
              Kompleksowa platforma e-commerce z zaawansowanymi funkcjami AI, real-time inventory management i progressive web app capabilities.
            </p>
            <div class="project-stats">
              <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-number">150%</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Wzrost konwersji</span>
              </div>
              <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-number">2.5s</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Czas ładowania</span>
              </div>
              <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-number">99.9%</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Uptime</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="project-actions">
              <a href="/projekty/ecommerce" class="btn btn-primary">
                <span>SZCZEGÓŁY</span>
              </a>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <span>LIVE DEMO</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project-card interactive" data-category="ai">
          <div class="project-visual">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3861958/pexels-photo-3861958.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="AI Analytics Dashboard" />
            <div class="project-overlay">
              <div class="overlay-content">
                <h3 class="project-title">AI Analytics Dashboard</h3>
                <p class="project-brief">Predykcyjny dashboard z machine learning</p>
                <div class="project-tech">
                  <span class="tech-tag">Python</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">TensorFlow</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">React</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-info">
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="project-type">AI & ANALYTICS</span>
              <span class="project-year">2024</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="project-name">AI Analytics Dashboard</h3>
            <p class="project-description">
              Zaawansowany dashboard analityczny wykorzystujący machine learning do predykcji trendów i automatycznej optymalizacji procesów biznesowych.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project-card interactive" data-category="blockchain">
          <div class="project-visual">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4164418/pexels-photo-4164418.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="DeFi Protocol" />
            <div class="project-overlay">
              <div class="overlay-content">
                <h3 class="project-title">DeFi Protocol</h3>
                <p class="project-brief">Zdecentralizowany protokół finansowy</p>
                <div class="project-tech">
                  <span class="tech-tag">Solidity</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">Web3</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">Next.js</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-info">
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="project-type">BLOCKCHAIN</span>
              <span class="project-year">2024</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="project-name">DeFi Protocol</h3>
            <p class="project-description">
              Innowacyjny protokół DeFi z automatycznym yield farming, liquidity mining i advanced tokenomics dla maksymalnej efektywności kapitału.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project-card interactive" data-category="mobile">
          <div class="project-visual">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3861969/pexels-photo-3861969.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Social Impact App" />
            <div class="project-overlay">
              <div class="overlay-content">
                <h3 class="project-title">Social Impact App</h3>
                <p class="project-brief">Platforma łącząca wolontariuszy</p>
                <div class="project-tech">
                  <span class="tech-tag">React Native</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">Firebase</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">GraphQL</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-info">
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="project-type">MOBILE APP</span>
              <span class="project-year">2024</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="project-name">Social Impact App</h3>
            <p class="project-description">
              Mobilna aplikacja społecznościowa łącząca wolontariuszy z organizacjami charytatywnymi w czasie rzeczywistym z geolokalizacją.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project-card interactive" data-category="web">
          <div class="project-visual">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1181263/pexels-photo-1181263.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Real Estate Platform" />
            <div class="project-overlay">
              <div class="overlay-content">
                <h3 class="project-title">Real Estate Platform</h3>
                <p class="project-brief">Platforma nieruchomości z VR tours</p>
                <div class="project-tech">
                  <span class="tech-tag">Next.js</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">WebXR</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">PostgreSQL</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-info">
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="project-type">REAL ESTATE</span>
              <span class="project-year">2024</span>
